The improved Veg-o-Matic
stretches food dollars.

948
01:04:50,616 --> 01:04:52,550
Millions bought at $ 7.77.

949
01:04:52,618 --> 01:04:54,848
Now yours for only $5.77.

950
01:04:54,921 --> 01:04:56,786
You'll save $2.00.!

951
01:04:56,856 --> 01:04:58,824
Where's your wallet at?

952
01:04:58,891 --> 01:05:00,722
Veg-o-Matic can cut
a whole, fiirm tomato...

953
01:05:00,793 --> 01:05:03,091
in one stroke.!

954
01:05:03,162 --> 01:05:05,960
That's my personal property.

955
01:05:06,032 --> 01:05:08,626
I'm going.

956
01:05:08,701 --> 01:05:12,102
Save $2.00 from the former price.

957
01:05:12,171 --> 01:05:15,402
Get one today for only $5.77.

958
01:05:19,378 --> 01:05:21,642
Let me give you...

959
01:05:21,714 --> 01:05:24,774
I got it. I got it.

960
01:05:30,923 --> 01:05:34,984
Hot dog!
Look what we got here.

961
